snippet.title: Andrew Klavan
snippet.description:
Andrew Klavan is the acclaimed author of such internationally bestselling crime novels as 'True Crime,' filmed by Clint Eastwood, and 'Don’t Say A Word,' starring Michael Douglas. He is the two-time winner and five-time nominee of the Edgar award for mystery writing. 

His YouTube channel features episodes and clips from The Andrew Klavan Show, a video podcast hosted by Drew as a part of The Daily Wire news and political opinion site.
